# MongoDB Data Layer

## Collections

`championships`, `seasons`, `players`, `matches`, `teams`, `admins`

## Embedding vs referencing

- **Embed** — per-match player stats inside `matches`
- **Cache** — aggregated per-season stats on `players`
- **Reference** — `season-id`, `championship-id`, `player-id` as ObjectIds

## Monger

- Connection/helpers: `galaticos.db.core`
- Use `monger.collection` for CRUD; `monger.operators` for `$set`, `$inc`, `$push`, `$elemMatch`, `$in`
- clj-kondo aliases these operators — see `.clj-kondo/config.edn`

## Aggregations

`src/galaticos/db/aggregations.clj` — Mongo cursors are **single-pass**; realize results before counting or re-iterating.

## Schema changes

When changing document shape:

1. Update `docs/reference/domain/mongodb-schema.md`
2. Add indexes in `config/database/init-indexes.js` if query paths change

## IDs

Convert string IDs to ObjectId via `galaticos.util.response/->object-id` at handler boundary, not ad hoc in every db fn.
